metadata.name: Fireworks
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Hulki Okan Tabak, Memorial for Death smart contract on Manifold, 2022

Memorial is a statue or structure established to remind people of a person or event, a statement of facts and a record

Death is the state of being dead and the personification of the power that destroys life.

The project has three parts that I will mint from. Snow covered part is a William Blake inspiration and touches upon death ever so slightly. Other parts are a cross between Auden inspirations and different visual experimentations. The artworks are created with artificial intelligence.
